                WriteLiteral(@"untu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"">For Visitors. </i><span style=""font-weight: 400;"">Linode may use Personal Data to send information about Linode to visitors and to contact such visitors. Linode also uses the information that it collects to improve the content of our website, enhance user experiences, and as training aids for our employees. Visitors have discretion as to whether to grant information to Linode, and may opt-out from such processes as outlined above</span>.</li>
